{"tid":715842,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]被曱甴爬過/咬過點算好？","createTime":"2018-06-24T20:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T02:52:30.000Z","uid":191453,"like":68,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"43245b61a3b0afce363ece8dc6c1aa1504b26801","tid":715842,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:22:23.000Z","msg":"啱啱黑媽媽側訓喺床上(上層) look連登<br />\n突然感覺到手臂比條毛hi過<br />\n本來以為係頭髮飄落嚟hi到<br />\n但係嗰感覺一路由手臂傳到去胳肋底<br />\n我即刻開閃光燈伸入衫入面睇下咩料啦<br />\n又冇發現啲乜wor<br />\n咁我就閂手機燈繼續look la<br />\n點知過咗一陣我一個轉身...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母大大隻曱甴黑影喺我床邊嗰扶手上面</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同個黑影對峙咗幾秒 <br />\n然後佢身手矯健咁爬咗去床尾嗰邊<br />\n我都唔執輸即刻從上格床跳咗落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轟一聲落完地<br />\n然後9衝去開燈順手抽咗好幾張紙巾<br />\n我一擰轉頭 <br />\n佢已經由右邊床尾爬咗上左邊牆上面<br />\n我一嘢踩上張櫈然後嚟手用紙巾包住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢嘅下場：又畀我包咗好幾浸紙巾然踩咗好多腳再沖咗落廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：身體比佢躝過，佢咁熟路我懷疑我琴晚大髀上面不知名傷口就係佢畀咬嘅...然後今晚食過返尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/041940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F041940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=431a468b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲我洗唔洗去疹所check check<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d660b84b6a3a2463ad3f3773ed822e38073ddf69","tid":715842,"uid":151836,"like":287,"dislike":1,"score":286,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:23:37.000Z","msg":"能力越大 責任越大"},{"pid":"92ec80d5fdf71f8a463817562918b1bbe63f61a3","tid":715842,"uid":171598,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedB