gmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同個黑影對峙咗幾秒 <br />\n然後佢身手矯健咁爬咗去床尾嗰邊<br />\n我都唔執輸即刻從上格床跳咗落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轟一聲落完地<br />\n然後9衝去開燈順手抽咗好幾張紙巾<br />\n我一擰轉頭 <br />\n佢已經由右邊床尾爬咗上左邊牆上面<br />\n我一嘢踩上張櫈然後嚟手用紙巾包住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢嘅下場：又畀我包咗好幾浸紙巾然踩咗好多腳再沖咗落廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：身體比佢躝過，佢咁熟路我懷疑我琴晚大髀上面不知名傷口就係佢畀咬嘅...然後今晚食過返尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/041940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F041940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=431a468b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲我洗唔洗去疹所check check<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:15:01.000Z","msg":"仆街我成日都有啲不知名傷痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌......."},{"pid":"c6db5d09bfc4bd6940f1225ea041f77d0b5e3646","tid":715842,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:19:52.000Z","msg":"佢背脊係似甲蟲殼, 定係一塊過透透地明?<br />\n如果透透地明個隻rip 定先....<br />\n你傷口個窿應該會越來越深...<br />\n紅色會越來越大..."},{"pid":"fa4cee41fe421a72434da136fa41a6544e60c402","tid":715842,"uid":47647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"要打破傷風針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce71fe36d355fe3477e0405aa19c437c7bf6699","tid":715842,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"係你手上播種"},{"pid":"8139db08b27940f1beacb524c56a8adf54b2f74f","tid":715842,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a16a27ccb1d82795fd98b67af724088622e122bf","tid":715842,"uid":88090,"like":0,"disli